		<h4 class="sprocket-lists-title padding" data-lists-toggler>
					Visiting Library Service 				<span class="indicator"><span>+</span></span>	</h4>
		<div class="sprocket-lists-item" data-lists-content>
		<div class="sprocket-padding">
						<p>The Library offers a Visiting Library Service for those who are unable to visit the Library due to health reasons and/or physical limitations. Please contact the Library at 905-899-1277 for more information.</p>					</div>
	</div>
</li>
<li data-lists-item>
		<h4 class="sprocket-lists-title padding" data-lists-toggler>
					Access Your Account Online 				<span class="indicator"><span>+</span></span>	</h4>
		<div class="sprocket-lists-item" data-lists-content>
		<div class="sprocket-padding">
						<p>Did you know that you can access your account online? Click on Catalogue (above), then click on My Account. Barcode is your Library Card number and password is your 7-digit telephone number (without area code).</p>					</div>
	</div>
</li>
<li data-lists-item>
		<h4 class="sprocket-lists-title padding" data-lists-toggler>
					Niagara Public Libraries Video				<span class="indicator"><span>+</span></span>	</h4>
		<div class="sprocket-lists-item" data-lists-content>
		<div class="sprocket-padding">
						<p><a href="https://vimeo.com/73896719" target="_blank">Check out this video about Your Niagara Public Library!</a></p>					</div>
	</div>
</li>
	</ul>
